so she shouldn't worry about the rumors and wait.

796
00:49:49,630 --> 00:49:53,220
Continue to print the flyer for a new member.

797
00:49:53,220 --> 00:49:56,220
Fighting! Ha Lee Chan, Fighting!

798
00:49:56,220 --> 00:49:58,680
I can't stand him. Seriously.

799
00:50:06,370 --> 00:50:07,860
Oh, my god!

800
00:50:08,580 --> 00:50:10,370
I'm...

801
00:50:10,370 --> 00:50:12,590
so sorry about yesterday.

802
00:50:14,000 --> 00:50:18,030
Wait! Could I join instead?

803
00:50:19,500 --> 00:50:20,970
I wonder what you're talking about.

804
00:50:20,970 --> 00:50:25,030
I meant the band. I'm a pretty good guitarist, actually.

805
00:50:25,030 --> 00:50:27,410
You provide free food and lodging, right?

806
00:50:27,410 --> 00:50:31,930
Could I stay at the boarding house instead of Yoon Dong Jin, by chance?

807
00:50:31,930 --> 00:50:35,510
My gosh, your skin must be made out of steel.

808
00:50:35,510 --> 00:50:37,240
I can't stay for long, either.

809
00:50:37,240 --> 00:50:40,330
- Until I figure out how to go back— 
 - Geez.

810
00:50:40,330 --> 00:50:42,760
Do you know what I went through because of you?

811
00:50:42,760 --> 00:50:44,050
Excuse me, could you—

812
00:50:44,050 --> 00:50:46,480
Other bands think we're scammers

813
00:50:46,480 --> 00:50:49,010
and I've lost credit with Se Kyeong.

814
00:50:49,010 --> 00:50:51,530
If only you didn't scam us that day,

815
00:50:51,530 --> 00:50:55,160
if only you didn't follow me, none of this crap would've happened.

816
00:50:55,160 --> 00:50:56,660
You know that?

817
00:50:57,500 --> 00:50:59,490
- Well, I'll make sure to— 
 - Shit.

818
00:50:59,490 --> 00:51:01,580
You'd better hide from now on.

819
00:51:01,580 --> 00:51:04,310
If I see even your hair, you're dead.

820
00:51:05,240 --> 00:51:08,090
- Don't be like that. Please— 
 - Don't follow me.

821
00:51:10,030 --> 00:51:12,020
Don't follow me, I said.

822
00:51:13,270 --> 00:51:14,680
I...

823
00:51:15,540 --> 00:51:17,820
have no place to go.

824
00:51:21,420 --> 00:51:22,890
Geez!

825
00:51:22,890 --> 00:51:25,330
H-Hold on a moment. Please.

826
00:51:27,890 --> 00:51:30,860
Hold on, hold on! Seriously...

827
00:51:31,770 --> 00:51:33,520
Se Kyeong.

828
00:51:36,490 --> 00:51:37,670
Did you hear the rumor?

829
00:51:37,670 --> 00:51:38,930
The rumor? What rumor?

830
00:51:38,930 --> 00:51:41,580
The boy who made a bet with you.

831
00:51:41,580 --> 00:51:44,080
Ha Lee Chan, the psycho from Baegwang High.

832
00:51:44,080 --> 00:51:45,330
What about him?

833
00:51:45,330 --> 00:51:47,900
He's been causing trouble trying to start a band,

834
00:51:47,900 --> 00:51:50,700
and he totally got destroyed this time.

835
00:51:50,700 --> 00:51:52,550
I'm glad it ended sooner than I thought.

836
00:51:52,550 --> 00:51:54,860
I know.

837
00:51:56,670 --> 00:51:59,640
What's this? A love letter?

838
00:52:03,280 --> 00:52:08,360
What? This is a ticket for Ji Hwan's band's show.

839
00:52:08,360 --> 00:52:10,200
Is this for me?

840
00:52:10,200 --> 00:52:12,970
I'm sorry, but...

841
00:52:12,970 --> 00:52:14,470
it's not for you.

842
00:52:15,300 --> 00:52:16,830
Where's mine, then?

843
00:52:16,830 --> 00:52:19,520
Who will you give that to?

844
00:52:59,490 --> 00:53:01,940
 I'm kind of disappointed about the new story. 

845
00:53:01,940 --> 00:53:04,730
 I was hoping for a twist. It's disappointing. 

846
00:53:47,480 --> 00:53:49,880
The bastard's like a wet leaf.

847
00:53:50,850 --> 00:53:52,950
I can't seem to get him off me.

848
00:53:56,010 --> 00:53:57,020
   

849
00:54:01,970 --> 00:54:03,620
Ha Lee Chan?

850
00:54:04,520 --> 00:54:06,850
Wow, Yong Joon Gi.

851
00:54:06,850 --> 00:54:08,540
Hey, damn!

852
00:54:08,540 --> 00:54:09,600
Do you go to this school?

853
00:54:09,600 --> 00:54:12,080
Yes. By the way, what happened? Is your...

854
00:54:12,080 --> 00:54:13,490
Is your band really over?

855
00:54:13,490 --> 00:54:16,030
I made a bet. I'm about to lose all of it—

856
00:54:16,030 --> 00:54:18,420
Ha Lee Chan!

857
00:54:19,910 --> 00:54:21,040
What's going on?

858
00:54:21,040 --> 00:54:22,190
I love you, Joon Gi.

859
00:54:22,190 --> 00:54:25,640
No, our relationship isn't like that, Lee Chan.

860
00:54:25,640 --> 00:54:28,450
No, Lee Chan. Hold on.

861
00:54:28,450 --> 00:54:29,980
Thank you for your hard work.

862
00:54:29,980 --> 00:54:31,870
Yes, okay.

863
00:54:32,980 --> 00:54:34,400
Hey, hold on.

864
00:54:35,630 --> 00:54:37,170
- Hold on. 
 - Lee Chan.

865
00:54:37,170 --> 00:54:39,100
- Come on. Come on. 
 - Ha Lee Chan!

866
00:54:39,100 --> 00:54:41,700
- Talk to me for a second. 
 - About what?

867
00:54:43,940 --> 00:54:45,650
   

868
00:54:45,650 --> 00:54:47,170
Okay.

869
00:54:50,080 --> 00:54:52,870
Hey, could you pass the ball?

870
00:54:55,580 --> 00:54:57,170
The left hand...

871
00:55:01,570 --> 00:55:04,840
- only supports— 
 - He's Baegwang High's Ha Lee Chan.

872
00:55:04,840 --> 00:55:06,300
Who's that? Is he a basketball player?

873
00:55:06,300 --> 00:55:09,130
I feel like I've heard of that name—

874
00:55:09,950 --> 00:55:11,720
Gosh.

875
00:55:11,720 --> 00:55:13,680
Damn it.

876
00:55:24,420 --> 00:55:27,360
Come here! Stop right there!

877
00:55:27,360 --> 00:55:29,730
Why are you so fast?

878
00:55:29,730 --> 00:55:31,480
Hey!

879
00:56:31,250 --> 00:56:34,570
 Geez, where did that bastard go? 

880
00:56:34,570 --> 00:56:37,650
 Gosh, did he go that way? 

881
00:56:47,040 --> 00:56:48,700
 Is he in here? 

882
00:56:51,530 --> 00:56:53,090
 Shit. 

883
00:57:06,550 --> 00:57:07,850
 Where's that coming from? 

884
00:57:07,850 --> 00:57:10,360
 I definitely heard something here. 

885
00:57:14,050 --> 00:57:16,870
Geez, why won't he come out?

886
00:57:32,650 --> 00:57:41,170


887
00:57:42,770 --> 00:57:45,370
Please stay like this.

888
00:57:45,370 --> 00:57:49,960
I'll make sure to return the favor before I die.

889
00:57:49,960 --> 00:57:55,460
♫  It's a new beginning, I breathe out  ♫

890
00:57:55,460 --> 00:57:57,270
Ahjumma?

