00:57:57,270 --> 00:57:59,810
♫  A moment I've been waiting for  ♫

892
00:57:59,810 --> 00:58:01,330
Ahjumma?

893
00:58:01,330 --> 00:58:03,670
Gosh, it's really Ahjumma.

894
00:58:05,930 --> 00:58:09,420
I never would've thought I'd meet you here. Really.

895
00:58:12,690 --> 00:58:15,620
♫  Don't look back, you won't have any regrets  ♫

896
00:58:15,620 --> 00:58:18,060
♫  No need to hesitate  ♫

897
00:58:18,060 --> 00:58:23,330
♫  This chance won't come again, so let's begin  ♫

898
00:58:23,400 --> 00:58:26,890
♫  The days that shone so bright  ♫

899
00:58:26,890 --> 00:58:30,550
♫  All our full dreams (shining, shining) just like now  ♫

900
00:58:30,550 --> 00:58:34,820
♫  Don't stop here like this, right now  ♫

901
00:58:34,820 --> 00:58:38,310
♫  Run without looking back  ♫

902
00:58:38,310 --> 00:58:43,720
♫  So you can dream again, higher, higher, fly higher  ♫

903
00:58:43,720 --> 00:58:47,770
♫  I hope this moment lasts forever  ♫

904
00:58:49,650 --> 00:58:52,350
♫  People are talking  ♫

